name: Global X All-Equity Asset Allocation Covered Call ETF
longDescription: The fund investing in exchange traded funds that provide exposure to a globally diversified portfolio of equity securities. To generate premiums, EQCC will be exposed to a dynamic covered call options writing program.
fulldescription: The fund investing in exchange traded funds that provide exposure to a globally diversified portfolio of equity securities. To generate premiums, EQCC will be exposed to a dynamic covered call options writing program. EQCC seeks to provide a combination of a high level of income and longterm capital growth
